        What Makes a Great Cannabis Dispensary?
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
        Not all cannabis dispensaries are created equal. Whether you're a medical patient seeking relief or a recreational user exploring options,
