          <li><strong>Personalized Recommendations:</strong> Ask about your needs, tolerance, and preferences before suggesting products</li>
          <li><strong>Patient Education:</strong> Take time to educate customers, especially first-time visitors</li>
          <li><strong>Transparent Communication:</strong> Honest about products, pricing, and what to expect</li>
          <li><strong>Professionalism:</strong> Courteous, respectful, and non-judgmental approach</li>
        </ul>

