        <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">4. Competitive and Transparent Pricing</h2>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
          While premium products command fair prices, great dispensaries balance quality with value and maintain transparent pricing practices.
        </p>

        <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-6 mb-3">Pricing Best Practices:</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-gray-700 mb-6">
          <li><strong>Clear Price Display:</strong> All products clearly marked with prices and potency</li>
          <li><strong>No Hidden Fees:</strong> Taxes and fees disclosed upfront</li>
          <li><strong>Regular Deals:</strong> Daily specials, happy hours, loyalty programs, or bulk discounts</li>
          <li><strong>Price Matching:</strong> Some top dispensaries offer competitive price matching</li>
          <li><strong>Medical Discounts:</strong> Special pricing for medical patients, veterans, seniors, or low-income individuals</li>
        </ul>

